query:
INSERT INTO machine_online_status (machineId, connectionId, isOnline, lastHeartbeat, lastDataReceived, currentCpk, currentMean, activeAlarmCount, warningCount, criticalCount, status, statusMessage)
VALUES 
(1, 1001, 1, NOW(), NOW(), 14500, 500000, 0, 0, 0, 'running', 'Đang hoạt động bình thường'),
(2, 1002, 1, NOW(), NOW(), 12800, 485000, 1, 1, 0, 'warning', 'CPK đang ở mức cảnh báo')
ON DUPLICATE KEY UPDATE 
isOnline = VALUES(isOnline),
lastHeartbeat = VALUES(lastHeartbeat),
currentCpk = VALUES(currentCpk),
status = VALUES(status);
